2 Installation
**************

PHP mode can be installed like any Emacs Lisp library.

   Download a source archive of the file.  It is available from PHP
mode's Web site.

   `http://php-mode.sourceforge.net/'

   Download either the file `php-mode-1.5.0.tar.gz' or
`php-mode-1.5.0.zip'.  Both source files have a respective GnuPG(1)
signature file with a .SIG file name extension.

